Project Report: Digital Literacy Awareness Infographic

I created my digital infographic using Canva, which is an easy and user-friendly design tool. My infographic focuses on the concept of digital literacy and highlights important areas such as useful digital tools, safe internet practices, professional online presence, and email etiquette.
The design is simple and clean, with clear headings and short bullet points to make the information easy to understand. I used basic icons and a minimal colour scheme to keep the infographic neat and visually appealing. The main aim of my design is to help students learn how to use technology safely, communicate properly, and maintain a positive online presence.
One challenge I faced was keeping the design simple while including all important points. Overall, this project helped me improve my creativity and understanding of digital literacy.

